<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2007—Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/110/140">Pub. L. 110–140</ref> substituted “noncontiguous domestic, or short sea transportation trade” for “or noncontiguous domestic trade”.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idf6d77461-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
